meta.title: WhatinApk - Your place for Android news and development info.
meta.description: We want to help you keep up with everything going on in the world of Android. From the latest news about your favorite Android devices to updates from Google and its partners and developers, Line's got you covered. In addition, we provide a wide range of resources to help you get the most out of your Android experience, including how-to guides, tutorials, answers to popular questions, community forums, and more.
